    "causal_summary": "The `external/` folder began as XCE research and now also contains the downloaded upstream cocoindex-code snapshot for the complete-fork prerequisite. Pt-01 produced the original code-graph + skill-advisor phases; pt-02 cross-validated those plans; pt-03 expanded scope to mcp-coco-index and the memory backend. Phase 001 was added on 2026-05-10 to replace the partial mcp-coco-index soft fork with a complete local fork of the upstream cocoindex-code MCP wrapper at v0.2.33, while keeping the transitive cocoindex engine as a pinned/audited dependency unless scope expands. The original phase children were renumbered to 002-011; CocoIndex-facing phases 007, 010, and 011 now depend on Phase 001 before modifying the MCP wrapper.",
